    "title": "Manufacturing Engineer - Netafim India - Top MNC",
    "description": "Netafim India has an exciting opening for a Manufacturing Engineer at our Bhubaneswar office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Netafim India:\nNetafim India is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage raw material procurement and inventory levels\n• Manage supplier quality audits and vendor development\n• Monitor equipment performance and coordinate preventive maintenance\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n• Maintain accurate production records and prepare daily reports\n• Ensure environmental compliance and waste management\n• Prepare production cost analysis and efficiency reports\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Bachelor's degree in a relevant field\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in SolidWorks\n• Proficiency in Six Sigma\n• Proficiency in GD&T\n• Proficiency in ISO 9001\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in Root Cause Analysis\n• Proficiency in Quality Control\n• Proficiency in Lean Manufacturing\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Flexible working hours\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhubaneswar, Odisha, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Netafim India!",
